**INTERVIEWER:** Staff Director L. Palacios
 
**INTERVIEWEE:** Jr. Rs. F. Ergot
##212325|No.##
**DATE:** 11 April 2022

-------

**PALACIOS:** Thank you for coming in - I understand that it has been a stressful time for you and I appreciate you taking the time to reach out.
###212325|//No, I can't be back here again.//##
**ERGOT:** Yeah.
###212325|You don't understand, it was over, I made sure it was over months ago.##
**PALACIOS:** Well, where would you like to start?
###212325|No - he doesn't get a chance to weep after all the things he said to me. Stop helping him.##
**ERGOT:** I haven't been sleeping again.
###212325|Stop. You know what you did. We //both// know.##
**PALACIOS:** Is it because of the nightmares? I thought those calmed down for a bit.
###212325|I haven't forgotten any of it. I remember it all.##
**ERGOT:** No, not those. Those haven't really stopped yet, by the way.
###212325|Am I in them? Stop doing that.##
**PALACIOS:** I'm sorry to hear - we could possibly up your zaleplon prescription if you bel-
###212325|"Such a good, obedient little boy." You think it's all a //joke?// You think it did //nothing?//##
**ERGOT:** It's not the nightmares.
###212325|Wait.##
**PALACIOS:** ...
 
**PALACIOS:** Oh, you mean that's not what's keeping you awake?
 
**ERGOT:** No, not this time around.
 
**PALACIOS:** May you elaborate?
 
**ERGOT:** ...
###212325|Don't.##
**ERGOT:** ...
###212325|Don't say it.##
**ERGOT:** ...I just...
 
**ERGOT:** ...
 
**ERGOT:** I think I keep seeing myself where I shouldn't be.
###212325|**//STOP//**##
**PALACIOS:** Oh? How so?
 
**ERGOT:** It's...
###212325|**//STOP STOP STOP STOP STOP//**##
**ERGOT:** ...
###212325|**//PLEASE STOP PLEASE STOP STOP FUCKING TALKING STOP TALKING I CAN'T DO THIS ANYMORE//**##
**ERGOT:** Sometimes when I have to go downstairs into the older archives, I see someone that has my own face, but it's different.
###212325|**//STOP FUCKING TALKING YOU'RE GETTING TOO CLOSE TO THE SURFACE STOP FUCKING TALKING//**##
**PALACIOS:** Is the appearance consistent? Can you describe him for me?
###212325|**//DON'T ASK HIM STOP PRYING STOP FUCKING TALKING ABOUT IT PLEASE STOP WHAT IF HE SEES WHAT IF HE SEES AND WHAT IF HE KNOWS//**##
**ERGOT:** Yes, actually. His hair is dirty blond and longer than mine. It's unkept and wavy.
###212325|**//SHUT UP SHUT UP SHUT UP SHUT UP SHUT UP SHUT UP STOP FUCKING TALKING __PLEASE__//**##
**ERGOT:** He also just...
###212325|**...**##
**ERGOT:** Whenever he sees me, he smiles.
###212325|**//__NO__//**##
**ERGOT:** And it's exactly the same.

**SCP-7478-2:**
[[=]]
[[size 620%]] **__//STOP//__** [[/size]]
[[/=]]
